All Implemented Interfaces:
BasicType<O>, Type<O>, Serializable, BasicValuedMapping, Bindable, DiscriminatorType<O>, JdbcMapping, JdbcMappingContainer, MappingModelExpressible, MappingType, SqlExpressible, ValueMapping, BasicDomainType<O>, DomainType<O>, ReturnableType<O>, SimpleDomainType<O>, BindableType<O>, OutputableType<O>, SqmExpressible<O>, SqmDomainType<O>, AdjustableBasicType<O>, BasicType<O>, ConvertedBasicType<O>, JavaTypedExpressible, ProcedureParameterExtractionAware<O>, ProcedureParameterNamedBinder<O>, Type
public class DiscriminatorTypeImpl<O> extends ConvertedBasicTypeImpl<O> implements DiscriminatorType<O>
Specialization of ConvertedBasicTypeImpl to expose access to the underlyingJdbcMapping of this discriminator - the bit that handles the relationship between the relational JavaType and the JdbcType
